message:
@ZAnimus Actually, the end of two eras. Quite a few of us came over from the old TSM forum.

I still tend to think of Take 2 as "the new thing".  It feels like yesterday that Neil and Renier came to visit me where I was working on the UWC campus to tell me about the new venture they were starting out on, and to discuss some technical details.  Over weak, bad coffee in the student centre caf, as I recall.

*sniff*
